title: Ragnar Benson Collection
description:
This is a collection of books authored by Ragnar Benson.

Currently this collection contains the following 21 books:

- Homemade C-4: A Recipe For Survival
- New And Improved C-4
- Ragnar's Guide To Home And Recreational Use Of High Explosives
- Ragnar's Homemade Detonators
- Home-Built Claymore Mines

- Ragnar's Big Book Of Homemade Weapons
- David's Tool Kit
- Breath Of The Dragon
- Homemade Grenade Launchers

- Mantrapping
- The Most Dangerous Game
- Ragnar's Ten Best Traps
- Survival Poaching

- Modern Weapons Caching
- The Modern Survival Retreat
- Ragnar's Urban Survival
- Live off the Land in the City and Country
- The Survival Retreat
- Survival Nurse
- Acquiring New ID
- Switchblade: The Ace Of Blades
